==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Curtal
<hw>Cur"tal</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A horse with a docked tail; hence,
anything cut short.</def> <mark>[Obs]</mark>
<rj><au>Nares.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

